insert  into `apartmani`(`id`,`naziv`,`postanskiBroj`,`karakteristike`,`opis`,`brojSoba`,`cijena`,`opisEng`,`korX`,`korY`) values (0,'Sole',21000,'wifi; klima','Suncem okupan, prema jugu orijentiran, pun svjetla, apartman Sole smjestio se u stambenoj zgradi u neposrednoj blizini hotela Radisson Blu i samo 5 min hoda od najljepših plaža grada Splita. Apartman je potpuno opremljen i moderno uređen, idealan za odmor i opuštanje, komforan za boravak četiri osobe i s mogućnošću smještaja još jedne osobe u boravku. Apartman se sastoji od dnevnog boravka, kuhinje, kupaonice s wc-em, dvije spavaće sobe sa lođom i pogledom na otoke Brač i Šoltu. Besplatan internet/ wi-fi. Sve što Vam treba naći ćete u krugu od 100m ( supermarket, pošta, ljekarna, banka, bankomat, kafići..). Za samo 7 min vožnje stići ćete do Dioklecianove palače, te trajektne luke, autobusnog i željezničkog',10,800,'Sun-drenched, south-oriented, full of light, apartment Sole is located in a building near the hotel Radisson Blu and only 5 minutes walk from the most beautiful beaches in the city of Split. The apartment is fully equipped and modern, ideal for rest and relaxation, comfortable room for four people and can accommodate one more person in the room. The apartment consists of a living room, kitchen, bathroom with WC, two bedrooms with a balcony and views of the islands of Brac and Solta. Free internet / wi-fi. All you need can be found within 100m (supermarket, post office, pharmacy, bank, cafes ..). In just 7 minutes drive you can reach the Diocletian\'s Palace, and the ferry port, bus and train station ...',43.507624,16.471883),(1,'Kokolo',21000,'wifi; klima; parking','\r\nApartman Kokolo nalazi se u starom djelu grada Splita, u kvartu Radunica. Tek je nekoliko minuta lagane šetnje udaljen od centra grada; rive, Dioklecijanove palače, pazara (tržnice), a da bi došli do najpopularnije splitske plaže Bačvice trebat će vam par minuta više. Apartman je kompletno nov i moderno opremljen. Posebnost apartmana je da se njegovih 45m2 smjestilo na 2 kata! U prizemlju se nalazi dnevni boravak sa televizijom te povećim kaučem na razvlačenje (na kojem mogu komodno prespavati dvije osobe), stol sa stolicama, kuhinja sa sudoperom, hladnjakom, štednjakom, aparatom za kavu, perilicom za rublje i glačalom. Na katu se nalazi kupaonica s tušem i dvokrevetna soba s krovnim prozorom. Kreveti po potrebi mogu biti spojeni ili razdvojeni. ',10,500,'Apartment Kokolo is located in the old part of the town, in the neighborhood Radunica. Only a few minutes walk from the city center, waterfront, Diocletian\'s Palace, bazaars (markets), and to get to the most popular beach in Split Bacvice you will need a few minutes more. The apartment is completely new and modern. The specialty suites that its 45m2 situated on two floors! On the ground floor there is a living room with a television and rather large sofa bed (where they can comfortably eat sleep two people), table with chairs, kitchen with sink, refrigerator, stove, coffee maker, washing machine and iron. Upstairs there is a bathroom with shower and a double bedroom with skylight. Beds can optionally be connected or separated. ',43.507129,16.445747),(2,'Lovre',21000,'wifi; klima; balkon; parking','Apartman se nalazi u jednom od najljepših dijelova Splita koji se zove Meje . Koji se nalazi praktički u centru grada, a istovremeno pruža mogućnost uživanja ​​u mirnoj i opuštajućoj atmosferi. Naš apartman nudi sve što je potrebno za savršen odmor, more je samo 50 m od kuće, prekrasna plaža Jadran je na 200 metara,a u radijusu od 500m postoje mnoge lijepe plaže. Do centra grada možete doći šetajuči jednom od najljepših šetnica uz more na Mediteranu. Nudimo vam vrlo komforan te veliki apartman. Sastoji se od 2 spavaće sobe, 1 dnevne sobe s jedaćim stolom, 1 kupatilom i kuhinjom. Jedna soba ima bračni krevet, dok je u drugoj prostrani krevet za jednu osobu, a u dnevnom boravku se nalazi dodatni ležaj za dvije osobe. ',10,600,'Welcome to Split, a 1700 years old town and the centre of Dalmatia! We offer everything that is needed for a perfect vacation. The sea is right outside the window, a beautiful beach called Jadran is 5 min away by foot and in the 500 m radius there are many more great beaches. Many other features are nearby, a supermarket is just a few doors down the street, the first cafe bar and restaurant are only 100 meters away and the center of the town is a merely 15 min walk. You can enjoy your walk to the center by one of the most beautiful seafront promenade of the Mediterranean. We offer you an extremely comfortable and wide space apartment. It consist of 2 bedrooms, a living room with a kitchen table, a bathroom and a kitchen. One bedroom offers a double bed, the other one a wide single bed, and in the living room there is an extra bed for two persons.',43.508628,16.440132),(3,'Luccari',20000,'wifi; balkon; parking','Dobro došli u nedavno obnovljeni, moderno uređeni, klimatizirani apartman koji se nalazi na izvrsnoj lokaciji! Svega 15 minuta hoda do starog, srednjovjekovnog dijela grada u kojem možete uživati u raznovrsnoj ponudi povijesnih lokaliteta, muzeja, restorana i kulturnih događanja. 10-ak minuta hoda do novog dijela grada s mnogobrojnim supermarketima, bankama, glavnim poštanskim uredom, lukom kao i glavnim autobusnim kolodvorom. Apartman Luccari sastoji se od spavaće sobe s bračnim krevetom, dnevnim boravkom sa sofom za dvije osobe, u potpunosti opremljenom kuhinjom i kupaonicom. Ispred apartmana nalazi se privatni parking s jednim osiguranim parkirnim mjestom za naše goste. ',-18,700,'Welcome to the newly refurbished, modern, air-conditioned apartment is situated in an excellent location! Only 15 minutes walk to the old, medieval part of town where you can enjoy the variety of available historical sites, museums, restaurants and cultural events. 10-minute walk to the new part of town with numerous supermarkets, banks, main post office, harbor and main bus terminal. Luccari apartment consists of bedroom with double bed, living room with sofa for two, fully equipped kitchen and bathroom. In front of the apartment there is private parking with one parking space for our guests.',42.649864,18.097545),(4,'Studio Prkacin',20000,'wifi; klima; balkon; parking','Apartmani Prkačin imaju dvije smještajne jedinice. Prva (studio apartman) A3+1 ima dvije spavaće sobe, kuhinju, kupaonicu s kadom, dnevnu sobu i veliki balkon sa direktnim pogledom na more i grad. Smještaj je za 4 osobe ako se koristi kauč u dnevnoj sobi. Apartman je opremljen SAT TV i klima uređajem. Ima privatni parking, a autobusna stanica je u blizini apartmana. Udaljenost od Starog grada je 600 m, a udaljenost od plaže 800 m. Druga smještajna jedinica (studio soba) A2 ima jednu spavaću sobu, kuhinju, tuš kabinu i predsoblje. Ima privatni parking.  Autobusna-stanica je u blizini. Studio je opremljen SAT TV i klima uređajem. Omogućuje smještaj za 2 osobe. Dubrovnik je bogat povijesnom i kulturnom baštinom. ',10,1000,'Apartments Prkačin have two units. The first (studio) A3 +1 has two bedrooms, a kitchen, a bathroom with bath, living room and large balcony with a direct view of the sea and the city. Accommodation for 4 people if used sofa in the living room. It is equipped with satellite TV and air conditioning. It has private parking and a bus stop is near the apartment. Old town is 600 m, and the distance from the beach 800 m Other accommodation units (studio rooms) 2 has one bedroom, kitchen, shower room and hallway. It has a private parking. The bus station is nearby. The studio is equipped with satellite TV and air conditioning. Allows accommodation for 2 people. Dubrovnik has a rich historical and cultural heritage',42.650955,18.099133),(5,'Naval Old Town',20000,'wifi; klima; parking','Apartman je smješten u mirnoj i širokoj ulici koja je paralelna s glavnom ulicom grada - Stradunom. U neposrednoj blizini su kavane, restorani, muzeji, galerije i sve glavne atrakcije grada. Stoga je to idealna lokacija za razgledavanje svega, kao i za noćni život. Jedna je plaža udaljena 4 min, a druga 15 min hoda. Tržnica i ulaz na zidine su na 2 minute hoda. Apartman je na II. katu kamene i vrlo uredne zgrade. Adaptiran je 2012. godine, a kuhinja i kupaona su još dodatno renovirane u proljeće 2014. g.',10,200,'The apartment is located in a quiet and wide street that is parallel to the main street of the town - Stradun. Close to cafes, restaurants, museums, galleries and all the major attractions of the city. Therefore, it is an ideal location for sightseeing and foremost, as well as nightlife. One beach is 4 minutes and the second 15 min walk. Market entry and the walls are a 2-minute walk away. The apartment is on the second. stone floor and a very neat building. Adapted the 2012th year, and kitchen and bathroom are additionally renovated in the spring of 2014. Mr.',42.640876,18.107638),(6,'Štinjan',52100,'wifi; klima; balkon','Pozivamo Vas da provedete ljetovanje u našim apartmanima. Apartmani se nalaze u mirnom mjestu Štinjan na jugozapadu Istre pokraj Pule. Pružaju predivan pogled na Nacionalni park Brijuni. Prostrani prostor, apartmani su potpuno opremljeni. Idealno mjesto za opuštanje. Osobito je privlačno za obitelji s djecom zbog prekrasne plaže. Samo 700 metara od mjesta je središnja plaža u Štinjanu. U samom mjestu ima sve što je potrebno za vaš odmor. Samo tri kilometara dalje u Puli se nalaze shopping centri, butici, restorani, caffe barovi, muzeji.',10,300,'We invite you to spend your holidays in our apartments. The apartments are located in a quiet place Štinjan the southwest of Istria, near Pula. Beautiful view of the Brijuni National Park. Spacious apartments are fully equipped. An ideal place to relax. It is particularly attractive for families with children because of its beautiful beaches. Just 700 meters from the central beach perfect vacation. The site has everything you need for your holiday. Just three miles away in Pula there are shopping centers, boutiques, restaurants, bars, museums',44.869225,13.85082),(7,'Golubic',52100,'wifi; klima; parking','Naša kuća i apartmani smješteni su turističkoj zoni “Veruda Porat”, mirnom predgrađu Pule. Svi apartmani imaju kompletno opremljenu kuhinju, kupaonicu, terasu sa roštiljem, SAT TV, klima uređaj. Objekt se nalazi cca 15 minuta hoda do plaže i oko 35 minuta hoda do centra. Veliki apartman Golubić za 5 ( max 7 )osoba od oko 70 m2 nalazi se u prizemlju kuće. Četiri apartman studija ( svaki oko 20 m2 ) su u samostalnom objektu iza kuće. Apartman 4 + 2 osobe 59 m2 je dvoetažni stan na drugom katu s dnevnim boravkom na donjem etaži i spavaćim prostorom (dva kreveta) na gornjoj etaži / galerija. Apartman za 2 + 2 osobe 35 m2, ima jednu spavaću sobu s bračnim krevetom i dnevni boravak sa kuhinjom i sa velikim kaučem. ',10,300,'Our houses and apartments are located in the tourist zone \"Veruda Porat,\" a quiet suburb of Pula. All apartments have fully equipped kitchen, bathroom, terrace with barbecue, satellite TV, air conditioning. The facility is located approximately 15 minutes walk to the beach and about a 35 minute walk to the center. Large apartment dove for 5 (max 7) a person of about 70 m2 and is located on the ground floor. Four studio apartments (each about 20 m2) in the separate building behind the house. Apartment 4 + 2 persons 59 m2 duplex apartment is on the second floor with a living room on the lower floor and bedroom (two beds) on the upper floor / gallery. Apartment for 2 + 2 persons 35 m2, one bedroom with a double bed and a living room with a kitchen and a large sofa.',44.848568,13.850382),(8,'Sršen',52100,'wifi; klima; balkon','Apartmani Sršen nalaze se na jednom od najatraktivnijih mjesta u Puli, svega 100m od poznate plaže Gortanova uvala. Kuća raspolaže sa 5 smještajnih jedinica; tri manja (od kojih jedan ima terasu za kaminom) i 2 veća apartmana. Vrt kuće ukrašavaju stabla mandarina i maslina. Okolicu okružuje borova šuma u kojoj se nalazim 2km duga trim staza. Sve bitne ustanove kao; pošta, ljekarna, banka, mjenjačnica, restoranit i dr. nalaze se svega max 400m od kuće.\r\n',10,500,'Apartments Fam. Sršen are located in one of the most attractive places in Pula, only 100m from the famous beach Gortanova uvala. The house has five apartments, three smaller (one of which has a terrace for the fireplace) and two larger suites. House garden its decorated with olive and tangerine trees. The countryside surrounds pine forest in which is the 2 km long jogging trail. All essential facilities like post, a pharmacy, bank, currency exchange, restaurant and other are on the distance of max. 400m from the house.',44.855496,13.831645),(9,'Villa Alice',52210,'wifi; klima; parking','VILLA ALICE se nalazi u uređenom i mirnom djelu grada Lamanova u Rovinju. Smještena je u blizini centra do kojeg ćete vrlo brzo stići i pješke. Objekt ima 4 nova i dobro opremljena apartmana. Kuća ima prekrasan vrt u kojem se nalazi roštilj. Osigurana su besplatna parking mjesta. Preporučuje se odlazak u centar bez automobila, 5-8 minuta lagane šetnje. Restorani, market, mesnica, frizerski salon, kozmetički salon nalaze se u neposrednoj blizini.',10,400,'Villa Alice is located in an ordered and peaceful suburb Lamanova in Rovinj. Situated near the center to which you will soon arrive on foot. The facility has 4 new and well equipped apartments. The house has a wonderful garden with a barbecue. Were provided free parking spaces. It is recommended to go to the center without a car, 5-8 minutes walk. Restaurants, supermarket, butcher, hairdresser, beauty salon located in the immediate vicinity.',45.082316,13.639597),(10,'Sandra',52210,'wifi; klima; balkon','Funkcionalno opremljen apartman, udaljen 20 minuta pješke do centra grada Rovinja, te 5-10 minuta automobilom do prvih plaža. Objekt se nalazi u zgradi na prvom katu, ima malu natkrivenu terasu sa pogledom na okolicu. Apartman ima opremljenu kuhinju sa posuđem, dvije sobe, wc i dnevni boravak sa tv - satom, DVD, radio. U blizini nalazi se kafić sa wi- fee. Jedna spavaća soba raspolaže sa bračnim krevetom dok je druga sa 2 ležaja(jednoležajni krevet). Posteljina i potrebni ručnici za vaš boravak čekat će vas spremni. Troškovi grijanja kao i korištenja klime uključeni su u cijenu. Za sve dodatne informacije slobodno nas kontaktirajte putem e - maila. Srdačno vas očekujemo i unaprijed želimo lijep odmor.',10,450,'Functionally furnished apartment, 20 minutes walk from the center of Rovinj, and 5-10 minutes by car to the first beach. The facility is located in the building on the first floor, has a small covered terrace with views of the countryside. The apartment has a fully equipped kitchen with utensils, two bedrooms, bathroom and living room with tv - clock, DVD, radio. Nearby there is a cafe with wi-fee. One bedroom has a double bed and the other with 2 beds (Single bed). Linens and towels needed for your stay you will be willing to wait. Heating costs as well as the use of climate are included in the price. For further information please contact us by e - mail. We wish you a nice vacation we advance',45.077943,13.654047),(11,'Slavko',52210,'wifi; klima; balkon; parking','Nalazimo se u mirnom dijelu grada,okruženi zelenilom, svega 10 minuta hoda od centra grada i 10 minuta od najbliže plaže. Naša kuća ima jedan veliki funkcionalno opremljen apartman,na dvije etaže površine 100m2 sa 4 parkirna mjesta i posebnim ulazom. Apartman se sastoji,od kuhinje sa balkonom, 2 kupaone, 3 spavaće sobe i dnevni boravak sa balkonom Za sve dodatne informacije slobodno nas kontaktirajte putem e-maila. Srdačno Vas očekujemo i želimo ugodan odmor.',10,370,'We are located in a quiet area, surrounded by greenery, just 10 minutes walk from the city center and 10 minutes from the nearest beach. Our house has a large functionally furnished apartment, 90m2 with 4 parking spaces and a separate entrance. The apartment comprises, kitchen with balcony, 2 bathrooms, 3 bedrooms with 2 single beds and a balcony, and a spacious living room also with balcony of the apartments can use the garden, grill and use of bicycles. For further information please contact us via e-mail. We sincerely wish you a pleasant holiday.',45.080606,13.647024);

