insert  into `hoteli`(`id`,`naziv`,`postanskiBroj`,`karakteristike`,`opis`,`brojSoba`,`cijena`,`opisEng`,`korX`,`korY`) values (0,'Atrium',21000,'wifi; klima; parking','S velikim vam ponosom predstavljamo Atrium hotel, mjesto savršenog odmora okrunjeno s 5 zvjezdica i smješteno u centru Splita.\r\n\r\nHotel Atrium, zdanje koje mramorom i staklom odražava modre boje mediteranskog neba, izrastao je na temeljima antičkog Splita, tik do lokacije koju je za svoj ljetnikovac odabrao slavni rimski car Dioklecijan. Akvedukt izgrađen u njegovo doba još se uvijek može vidjeti u izložbenom prostoru u podzemnim prostorijama hotela. Od hotela do Diklecijanove palače, samog srca antičkog Splita, te do vedre i uvijek prepune rive pješači se svega petnaestak minuta – toliko smo blizu epicentra svih događanja u Splitu.',50,350,'We are proud to present Atrium hotel, a place for a perfect vacation, crowned with 5 stars and located in the centre of Split, Croatia.\r\n\r\nAtrium hotel, one of the best hotels in Split is a building that reflects the blue Mediterranean sky with its marble and glass, has grown on the foundations of ancient Split, just next to the location that the famouse Roman emperor Diocletian chose as his summer house. Aqueduct bulit in that era can be seen in the official exhibit site, at the underground premises of the hotel. From the hotel to the Diocletian’s palace and the vibrant and crowded waterfront is a fifteen minutes walk – we are that close to the epicentre of all the events in Split.',43.510538,16.439362),(1,'Globo',21000,'wifi; balkon; parking','Hotel Globo otvoren je 2001. godine i smatra se jednim od najluksuznijih i najbolje opremljenih hotela u gradu Splitu. Hotel Globo nalazi se u uskom središtu grada nadomak svim pravnim i kulturnim institucijama kao i gradskim plažama, što predstavlja veliku prednost ovog zdanja. Do predivne gradske šetnice uz more, poznate kao omiljeno sastajalište Splićana svih generacija dijeli vas tek desetak minuta lagane šetnje kroz povijesnu jezgru grada Splita.',50,250,'Hotel Globo has been erected in 2001 and is considered as one of the most luxurious hotels in Split since it has the best equipment. The hotel Globo is situated in the centre of the city, at only few steps from all public and cultural institutions, but also from the city-s beaches, the fact that represents a big advantage of staying in this hotel. At only ten minutes of walk through the historic centre of Split you will find yourself on the famous promenade with palm trees and a series of bars which are the favourite meeting place of Split\'s population.',43.515456,16.439735),(2,'Radisson',21000,'wifi; klima; balkon; parking','Smješten na jednoj od prekrasnih šljunčanih plaža Jadranskog mora, udaljen svega 3 km od centra grada Radisson Blu Resort, Split omogućava savršenu ravnotežu između luksuznog mirnog odmora i avantura po jadranskoj obali.\r\n\r\nRadisson Blu Resort, Split nudi 250 soba, od kojih je svaka dizajnirana s posebnom pažnjom. Većina soba nudi pogled na more, s luksuznim uređenjem, opremljene flat screen televizorima, pristupom brzom bežičnom internetu, mini bar-om i ostalim.',50,200,'Located on one of the Adriatic coast\'s picturesque pebble beaches only 3 km from the city center, Radisson Blu Resort, Split strikes the perfect balance between a luxurious secluded retreat and a vitalizing adventure in the Dalmatian coast. Radisson Blu Resort, Split offers you 250 rooms, each designed with special care. The majority of our rooms overlook the Adriatic sea and are luxuriously furnished, equipped with flat screen TV, access to free hi speed wireless internet, mini bar, etc.',43.503072,16.470977),(3,'Bellevue',20000,'wifi; klima; parking','Na samoj litici zaljeva Miramare smjestio se luksuzni hotel Bellevue Dubrovnik. Udaljen svega 800 metara od Starog grada u Dubrovniku a opet izoliran od buke grada predstavlja idealan smještaj za one koje žele provesti svoj odmor u oazi mira.\r\n\r\nLuksuzni interior hotela odražava se i na sobe kojih ima 91, uključujući 14 apartmana i predsjednički apartman. Sve sobe hotela Bellevue Dubrovnik su luksuzne, pažljivo uređene sa posebnim detaljima dajući Vam do znanja da ste u hotelu koji je proglašem jedan od najboljih novih hotela u Europi od strane novina \"The Sunday Times\". ',50,500,'On a clifftop, 30 meters above the Miramare bay and just 800 meters from the Old Town of Dubrovnik lies the luxury 5 star hotel, Hotel Bellevue, a veritable sanctuary for people who seek to relax their spirit and awaken senses, escaping from the haste of everyday life. \r\n\r\nHotel Bellevue features 91 rooms, including 14 suites and the president suite. All facilities in hotel Bellevue Dubrovnik are luxuriously and carefully decorated with special details, making sure that the guests feel that they are in one of the best newly opened hotels in Europe (evaluated by the journalists of “The Sunday Times”)',42.651302,18.061175),(4,'Excelsior',20000,'wifi; klima; balkon; parking','Hotel Excelsior Dubrovnik jedan je od najpoznatijih i najluksuznijih hotela na Mediteranu. Zbog svoje atraktivne lokacije ovaj hotel sa 5 zvjezdica predstavlja vrh ponude hotela na Jadranu.\r\n\r\nSobe (141) i apartmani (17) hotela Excelsior luksuzno su uređeni sa probranim detaljima i vrhunskim interijerom. Moderno opremljene sadrže : flat SAT-TV, wifi internet, pay TV, mini bar, sef, orgtač i papuče, usluge sa VIP tretmanom, telefon, ekskluzivna kozmetika itd. Očaravajući pogled na staru gradsku jezgru, more i susjedne otoke nikoga neće ostaviti ravnodušnim.\r\n\r\nHotel Excelsior Dubrovnik na raspolaganje svojim gostima nudi privatnu plažu u kojoj u miru možete uživati u čarima kristalno čistog mora.',50,450,'Dubrovnik Hotel Excelsior is known as one of the finest hotels on the Mediterranean. Due to its attractive location, this luxury five-star hotel represents one of the best hotels in the Adriatic. \r\n\r\nExcelsior Hotel Dubrovnik has 141 luxury bedrooms and 17 suites that are all equipped with: flat SAT – TV, wifi internet, pay TV, mini bar, safe, bathrobes and slippers, with the VIP treatment, telephone, exclusive cosmetics, etc. An outstanding seafront position with stunning hotel views on the Old Town with Dubrovnik fortresses and the island of Lokrum makes a person feel calm and relaxing pulse of the Adriatic that nobody can resist. \r\n\r\nThe guests of the Hotel Excelsior Dubrovnik have at their disposal a private beach where they can enjoy the magic crystal clear sea.',42.641323,18.118674),(5,'Palace',20000,'wifi; klima; balkon; parking','Hotel Dubrovnik Palace smješten je na prelijepoj lokaciji na mirnom poluotoku Lapad, okružen Petka šumom s veličanstvenim pogledom na more i Elafitske otoke. Hotel se nalazi blizu povijesne jezgre starog grada Dubrovnika. Izoliran od gradske vreve, i okružen morem i borovom šumom, Hotel Dubrovnik Palace je idealno mjesto za goste koji traže privatnost i opuštanje.\r\n\r\nJedinstvene kaskadne arhitekture, Hotel Dubrovnik Palace ima 308 luksuznih soba i apartmana s privatnim balkonom i spektakularnim pogledom na more. Pažljivo izabrani materijali, poput kvalitetnog drva, sagova i prirodnog kamena baza su bogatog interijera punog stila. Zbog jedinstvenog kaskadnog arhitektonskog rješenja hotela Dubrovnik Palace, svaka od 308 luksuznih soba i apartmana ima privatni balkon i spektakularan pogled na more. \r\n',50,400,'Hotel Dubrovnik Palace resides on a beautiful peninsula called Lapad, below the park of little Petka woods, with a unique view to the Elaphite islands. The Hotel is located near the historic center of the old town Dubrovnik. Isolated from the urban turbulence, surrounded by the sea and pine woods, Hotel Dubrovnik Palace is ideally located to meet guests that seek privacy and relaxation.\r\n\r\nThe Hotel Dubrovnik Palace’s unique cascading architecture allows that all 308 sumptuous rooms and suites have a private balcony and spectacular sea view',42.648132,18.082447),(6,'Brioni',52100,'wifi; klima; balkon','Hotel Brioni Pula, udaljen četiri kilometra od povijesnog centra grada Pule, smješten je naspram mora i uronjen u zelenilo prirode, te povezan s morem terasastim plažama. Sam hotel nalazi se u turističkom naselju Verudela. Hotel Brioni se sastoji od četiri dijela i ima 222 sobe rasporeďene na 3 kata ukusno i udobno namještene te od nedavno obnovljene, s telefonom i satelitskom TV. Hotel Brioni ima prostrane terase s vanjskim bazenom i jednim unutarnjim grijanim bazenom, oba s morskom vodom, te sauna i masaža. Dnevni, zajednički prostori hotela klimatizirani su, a čini ih recepcija, prostrani dnevni boravak, konferencijska dvorana s 200 mjesta, TV sala, restoran, aperitiv bar i diskoteka. Gosti hotela Brioni mogu koristiti teniske terene, mini golf i ostale sportske sadržaje.\r\n\r\n',50,300,'Hotel Brioni Pula is four kilometers away from the historic center of Pula, and has an amazing beachfront. The hotel is situated in Verudela vacation village, surrounded by greenery on one side and beautiful beaches on the other. Hotel Brioni consists of four buildings and has 222 rooms tastefully and comfortably renovated and located on three floors. Each room is equipped with SAT/TV and telephone. Hotel Brioni has extensive terraces, an outdoor swimming-pool and a heated indoor pool, both with sea water, also equipped with a sauna and massage center. Hotel Brioni has a sitting room by the reception, a conference hall with 200 seats, a TV hall, restaurant, aperitiv bar, and a disco bar, all of them are air conditioned. Tennis courts, mini-golf, and all other sports activities are available to hotel guests.',44.835706,13.834929),(7,'Galija',52100,'wifi; klima; parking','Galija, mali obiteljski hotel, nalazi se na jugu Istarskog poluotoka u strogom centru 3000 godina stare Pule. Suvremeno opremljen, svojim gostima nudi ugodan boravak tokom cijele godine. Hotel Galija svojom uslugom orijentiran je prema turistima, putnicima i poslovnim ljudima, te manjim grupama s mogučnošću organizacije poslovnih domjenaka i stručnih seminara.\r\n\r\nNaš restoran Galija izvor je istarskih, mediteranskih i internacionalnih specijaliteta koji povezuju tradiciju i umijeće naših kuhara. \r\nNudimo i vrhunske pizze iz peći na drva.\r\n',50,270,'Galija, a small family hotel located on the south of the Istrian peninsula in centre of the 3000 year old town of Pula. Modernly equipped, it offers a pleasant stay to its guests all year round. Hotel Galija is oriented towards tourists, travellers and business people. It offers the possibility of organizing small business banquets and business seminars. \r\n\r\nOur restaurant is the source of Istrian, Mediterranean and international cuisine that binds tradition and proficiency of our chefs.\r\nWe offer homemade pizzas from a wood-fired oven.',44.864613,13.849277),(8,'Histria',52100,'wifi; klima; balkon; parking','Prikladno smješten (u blizini zračne luke) u mjestu Pula, objekt Park Plaza Histria Pula nalazi se u blizini znamenitosti plaža Punta Verudela, utvrda Bourguignon i Mornaričko groblje. U blizini su i Forum te Augustov hram.\r\n\r\nObjekt Park Plaza Histria Pula ima mnogo sadržaja, a osobito su ugodni: vanjski bazen, unutarnji bazen i parna kupelj. Bežični internet besplatan je u javnim prostorima. Hotel (prikladno za obitelj) gostima nudi brojne pogodnsoti, među kojima su i: 3 kafić(a)/kavana(e), bar pokraj bazena te bar/salon. Gostima se svako jutro poslužuje besplatan doručak. Osoblje može dogovoriti da na raspolaganju budu organizacija turističkog obilaska/kupnje ulaznica i usluge vjenčavanja. Dodatne su pogodnosti: sezonski vanjski bazen, dječji bazen i noćni klub. Parkiranje na lokaciji je besplatno.\r\n \r\n',50,375,'Conveniently near the airport in Pula, Park Plaza Histria Pula is close to Punta Verudela Beach, Fort Bourguignon, and Naval Cemetery. Also nearby are Forum and Temple of Augustus. Park Plaza Histria Pula has an outdoor pool, an indoor pool, and a steam room. Wireless Internet access is complimentary in public areas. Dining options at this family-friendly hotel include 3 coffee shops/cafés, a poolside bar, and a bar/lounge. Guests are served a complimentary breakfast each morning. The staff can provide tour/ticket assistance and wedding services. Additional amenities include a seasonal outdoor pool, a children\'s pool, and a nightclub. Onsite parking is complimentary. This is a smoke-free property.',44.869401,13.858095),(9,'Eden',52210,'wifi; parking','Smješten blizu plaže u mjestu Rovinj, objekt Maistra Eden Hotel Rovinj nalazi se u blizini znamenitosti luka Rovinj, Trg m. Tita i otok Sveta Katarina. U blizini su i Trg Valdibora te crkva sv. Eufemije.\r\n\r\nObjekt Maistra Eden Hotel Rovinj ima mnogo sadržaja, a osobito su ugodni: vanjski teniski tereni, zatvoreni teniski tereni i unutarnji bazen. Besplatan bežični pristup internetu dostupan je u javnim prostorima. Ovaj spa hotel ima bar pokraj bazena i bar/salon. Gostima se služi besplatan doručak. Dodatne su pogodnosti: sezonski vanjski bazen, dječji bazen i dječji klub. Uz nadoplatu, gosti mogu koristiti prijevoz do i od zračne luke (dostupno na zahtjev). Parkiralište za goste je besplatno. Ovo je objekt u kojem se ne puši.',50,400,'Situated near the beach in Rovinj, Hotel Lone is close to Rovinj Harbour, Sveta Katarina, and Trg Marsala Tita. Also nearby are Trg Valdibora and St. Euphemia\'s Church. Hotel Lone has a full-service spa, an outdoor pool, and an indoor pool. Wireless Internet access is complimentary in public areas. Business amenities at this 5-star property include a business center and small meeting rooms. The hotel offers 3 restaurants along with 4 coffee shops/cafés and a bar/lounge. Guests are served a complimentary breakfast each morning. The staff can provide tour/ticket assistance and wedding services. Additional amenities at this Beaux Arts hotel include a nightclub, a spa tub, and a fitness center. For a surcharge, guests have access to a roundtrip airport shuttle (available on request). Onsite parking is offered for a surcharge. This is a smoke-free property.',45.073039,13.640942),(10,'Park',52210,'wifi; klima; parking','Smješten blizu plaže u samom centru mjesta Rovinj, objekt Maistra Park Hotel Rovinj nalazi se u blizini znamenitosti: luka Rovinj, otok Sveta Katarina i Trg m. Tita. U blizini su i Trg Valdibora te crkva sv. Eufemije.\r\n\r\nPogodnosti u hotelu \r\nObjekt Maistra Park Hotel Rovinj ima mnogo sadržaja, a osobito su ugodni: marina, unutarnji bazen i sauna. Javni prostori opremljeni su internetom velike brzine (žičanim) (primjenjuju se nadoplate). Hotel u mjestu Rovinj ima mnogo sadržaja, među kojima su kavana/kafeterija i bar pokraj bazena. Gostima se svako jutro poslužuje besplatan doručak. Dodatne su pogodnosti: sezonski vanjski bazen, dječji bazen i centar za fitness. Uz nadoplatu, gosti mogu koristiti prijevoz do i od zračne luke (dostupno na zahtjev). Parkiralište za goste je besplatno.\r\n',50,320,'Situated near the beach in the heart of Rovinj, Maistra Park Hotel Rovinj is close to Rovinj Harbour, Sveta Katarina, and Trg Marsala Tita. Also nearby are Trg Valdibora and St. Euphemia\'s Church. Maistra Park Hotel Rovinj has a marina, an indoor pool, and a sauna. Public areas are equipped with high-speed (wired) Internet access (surcharges apply). This Rovinj hotel offers a coffee shop/café and a poolside bar. Guests are served a complimentary breakfast each morning. Additional amenities include a seasonal outdoor pool, a children\'s pool, and a fitness center. For a surcharge, guests have access to a roundtrip airport shuttle (available on request). Guest parking is complimentary.',45.076092,13.63723),(11,'Valdaliso',52210,'wifi; klima; balkon; parking','Smješten blizu plaže u mjestu Rovinj, objekt Maistra Hotel Valdaliso nalazi se u blizini znamenitosti crkva sv. Eufemije, Trg Valdibora i Trg m. Tita. U blizini su i luka Rovinj te otok Sveta Katarina.\r\n\r\nPogodnosti u objektu. \r\nResort (prikladno za obitelj) nudi mnogo sadržaja, a osobito su udobni restoran i bar/salon. Besplatan doručak poslužuje se svako jutro. Javni prostori opremljeni su internetom velike brzine (žičanim) (primjenjuju se nadoplate). Dodatne su pogodnosti: dječji klub, prostor za zabavne i videoigre i višejezično osoblje. Parkiralište za goste je besplatno.\r\n',50,280,'Situated near the beach in Rovinj, Maistra Hotel Valdaliso is close to St. Euphemia\'s Church, Trg Valdibora, and Trg Marsala Tita. Also nearby are Rovinj Harbour and Sveta Katarina. Dining options at this family-friendly resort include a restaurant and a bar/lounge. A complimentary breakfast is served each morning. Public areas are equipped with high-speed (wired) Internet access (surcharges apply). Additional amenities include a children\'s club, an arcade/game room, and multilingual staff. Guest parking is complimentary.',45.102263,13.624699);

